text.tspan: Output of key service and industrial sectors in the United Kingdom,
This data is indexed to the year 1700. It shows how much output was produced relative to that in 1700.
Data source: Broadberry, S., Campbell, B. M., Klein, A., Overton, M., & Van Leeuwen, B. (2015)
Note: Data before 1700 refers to England, later data refers to United Kingdom.
